      "content": "i was just looking at the stars and it hit me how much of a joke everything is. the universe is just expanding into nothingness, and in a few billion years none of this—not my pain, not my life, not anything—will even be a memory. it all feels so incredibly pointless. why even bother trying to keep going when the end result is just... nothing?",
